title: Lee Keun-ho (footballer, born 1996)
text: Lee Keun-ho (; born 21 May 1996) is a South Korean <a href="football%20%28soccer%29">football</a> <a href="Forward%20%28association%20football%29">forward</a> who plays for <a href="Jeju%20United%20FC">Jeju United</a> in <a href="K%20League%201">K League 1</a>.
